      "id": "aaaaaaaa-0000-4000-8000-000000000009",
      "name": "List Issues",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [
        380,
        80
      ],
      "credentials": {
        "oAuth2Api": {
          "id": "",
          "name": "SAP S/4HANA (PS/PPM Financials — read-only) account"
        }
      },
      "notes": "Actual-cost line items for a WBS element, from the released CDS view I_ProjectActualCosts (backed by the universal journal, table ACDOCA) — filtered to the WBS/cost object scoped by projectId. Budget/plan figures are NOT on this view: they live on the separate financial-planning service API_FINPLANNINGDATA_SRV (backed by ACDOCP), which is intentionally not auto-wired here (different filter keys/cadence) — add it as a second HTTP node in the generated workflow if you need plan-vs-actual in one pass. CONFIRM the exact OData path your tenant has published I_ProjectActualCosts under (Gateway service catalog, transaction /IWFND/MAINT_SERVICE) before importing: CDS-view analytical services are frequently republished under a generated 'srvd_a2x' service id that varies by SAP release/component version — the path below is the documented v2-style wrapper convention, not a guarantee for your system."
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "={{ $env.SAP_S4_URL }}/sap/opu/odata/sap/API_ENTERPRISE_PROJECT_SRV/A_EnterpriseProjectElement?$select=ProjectUUID,WBSElementInternalID,WBSElement,WBSElementDescription,ControllingArea,CompanyCode,ResponsibleCostCenter&$format=json",
        "sendHeaders": false,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": []
        },
        "options": {},
